I have been completely unfaithful to you. I have not been committed to you, journal, the way i promised. Well, the dry spell is over. I am starting today. Again.
Post from mobile portal m.livejournal.com

Friends only!

If you'd like to read or continue to read my journal: add me or create an account.

Quick little Bio:

Name: Jenavette
Age: 22
Status: Happy

By the way I've added my other livejournal to rough draft my short stories at shortstoryjena. That journal is friends only and holds no bias. You can be just about anyone!
